description: Searches for Amazon Braket jobs that match the specified filter values.

parameters.name: filters
parameters.description: The filter values to use when searching for a job. (dict) --- A filter used to search for Amazon Braket jobs. The name to use for the jobs filter. An operator to use for the jobs filter. The values to use for the jobs filter. (string) ---

nested_params.name: name
nested_params.description: The name to use for the jobs filter.

nested_params.name: operator
nested_params.description: An operator to use for the jobs filter.

nested_params.name: values
nested_params.description: The values to use for the jobs filter.

nested_items.name: jobs
nested_items.description: An array of JobSummary objects for devices that match the specified filter values.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the Amazon Braket job was created.

nested_items.name: device
nested_items.description: Provides summary information about the primary device used by an Amazon Braket job.

nested_items.name: endedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the Amazon Braket job ended.

nested_items.name: jobArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the Amazon Braket job.

nested_items.name: jobName
nested_items.description: The name of the Amazon Braket job.

nested_items.name: startedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time that the Amazon Braket job was started.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the Amazon Braket job.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token used for pagination of results, or null if there are no additional results. Use the token value in a subsequent request to continue results where the previous request ended.
